        <li>Swedish massage</li>
        <li>refreshing foot massage</li>
        <li>healing massage</li>
        <li>maternity, baby massage</li>
        <li>kinesio tapeing</li>
      </ul>
      <p>I have completed several Prana-nadi courses and have mastered the techniques of Kinesio tape. I’ve been
        training myself professionally, physically, mentally and spiritually.</p>
      <p>I got my work experience among VIP sections of the Széchenyi Spa, and in Hotel Gellért. I worked at Magnolia
        Day Spa. Currently I work as a private entrepreneur, mostly 4 and 5 stars hotels, wellness, office buildings,
        with families and individuals. In 2017 I provided massages for athletes with my colleagues at international
        beach volleyball at Siófok. We also gave service at VIP Plage massage in Siofok.</p>
      <p>Trust, accuracy, purity, external and internal harmony are the most important values for me.</p>
      <p>If you want a reliable masseuse in your office or home, please contact me via e-mail or phone. I’m working
